==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Operand
<hw>Op"er*and</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From neuter of L.
<ets>operandus</ets>, gerundive of <ets>operari</ets>. See
<er>Operate</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>The symbol, quantity,
or thing upon which a mathematical operation is performed; -- called
also <altname>faciend</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Operant</ent>⟦br⟧
